org.apache.streams.instagram.provider

Class InstagramDataCollector<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.streams.instagram.provider.InstagramDataCollector<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Runnable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    InstagramCommentsCollector, InstagramEngagersCollector, InstagramLikersCollector, InstagramRecentMediaCollector, InstagramUserInfoCollector

    public abstract class InstagramDataCollector<T>
extends Object
implements Runnable
    Executes on all of the Instagram requests to collect the Instagram data.

    If errors/exceptions occur when trying to gather data for a particular user, that user is skipped and the collector move on to the next user. If a rate limit exception occurs it employs an exponential back off strategy.
